I know that this isn't my main goal of landing on Eve, but last night I landed a rover on the mun, properly. Considering this is the third time that my kerbonaut has survived a mun encounter and the first time the vehicle also survive, I am quite proud of myself. I did this with no mods

http://imgur.com/a/JVlky

Two screenshots, first one is my victory shot, the second is wheelies, on the mun.... ya know, for science.
